tsadwyn is a TypeScript port of Cadwyn (https://github.com/zmievsa/cadwyn),
originally created by Stanislav Zmiev. The head-first API versioning model,
the declarative VersionChange DSL, the schema/route regeneration pipeline,
and the carefully thought-out documentation that made this port even possible
are all his work. Enormous thanks to Stanislav for designing and open-sourcing
such an elegant solution to a genuinely hard problem — his work is awesome.

